{"tid":475050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國球迷奪\"藏獨\"旗遭阻攔 德足協:這算言論自由","createTime":"2017-11-20T17:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T05:11:39.000Z","uid":5195,"like":123,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"11cdc2701f8321d80fb93d3d15244d8721e600b9","tid":475050,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"當地時間18日，中國足協U20選拔隊球員以客隊身份，首次參加在美因茨舉行的德國西南地區聯賽。比賽中，觀眾席上有人掛出&ldquo;藏獨&rdquo;旗幟，中方隊員隨即退出賽場。一名中國球迷衝上前去試圖奪走&ldquo;藏獨&rdquo;旗遭到阻攔。<br />\n<br />\n這名奪旗的球迷在社交工具上表示：&ldquo;足球是個團體項目，德國這方面很強！希望能夠讓U20好好在德國鍛煉，回來報效祖國！我在現場看比賽因為這事兒停了，一著急想都沒想就過去搶'藏獨'旗子去了，結果被媒體拍了!&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而德國足協主席副主席齊默爾曼在賽后接受采訪時表示這屬於&ldquo;言論自由&rdquo;：&ldquo;我們當然想成為好東道主，所以對出現的情況不是很愉快。我們在比賽前已提示過中國代表團，在德國體育場館里人們享有自由表達觀點的權利，包括言論自由。我們認為，在球場內打出這樣的旗幟也是屬於這個範疇的。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"4f22c9fb75fdfb04e5f4cd0332b8c9b110c056fa","tid":475050,"uid":19762,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/news/2017/11/20/TELEMMGLPICT000147061103_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqyWpBy-fni92heetr3tbm7qaAqcfQcNNU9wB1mYhms7A.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fnews%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2FTELEMMGLPICT000147061103_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqyWpBy-fni92heetr3tbm7qaAqcfQcNNU9wB1mYhms7A.jpeg&h=94bc0a38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d1137bf7fbb0b6c279f00c1ea63588579662cd3","tid":475050,"uid":389,"like":25,"dislike":4,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:06:22.000Z","msg":"香港咁做係辱華"},{"pid":"602e62bfaaa1c9166a6bce476705737468935fde","tid":475050,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T18:06:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026f325e7676c86a459512b12b6625e4f5deb799","tid":475050,"uid":2854,"like":51,"dislike":2,"scor